	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunciavit mihi affinis meus (reverende in Christo pater) tuis verbis res in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> recte se habere; scripsit idem d. legatus, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8160">de Bellieure</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Id mihi periucundum fuit audire.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri tandem nactus sum integra concilii <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentini</placeName>; etsi autem invitus dimitto, tamen tibi mitto; si habes iam ante, aliquando remitte; sin minus retine, cura tamen, ut <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1227" cert="high">Froscoverus</persName> aliquot exemplaria <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l157" cert="high">Francoforto</placeName> advehat, ut inde reparare possim.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exierunt praeterea <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l522">Venetiis</placeName> disputationes adversarii mei <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispani</placeName>, cuius hic titulum mitto, sed liber integer ad me non venit, quod pessime me habet; desiderantur enim quaedam folia.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Est additus libellus de traditionibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque monendus erat <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1227" cert="high">Froscoverus</persName>, ut haec quoque exemplaria pro amicis afferat.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">An rediturus sit <persName type="auto_name">Philippi</persName> legatus, prout constanter ferebatur, dubito; nihil hic certi affirmare possum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Cardinalis Madrucius</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Cristoforo oder Ludovico Madruzzo.</note> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425">Roma</placeName> cum mala pontificis gratia discessisse fertur; sic <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8114">Balingketus</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName> audivit, tamen causa offensae in tam parva mora resciri nondum potuit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hannibalis miles versatur in agro <placeName type="auto_name">Cremonensi</placeName>; conscribitur quoque in agro <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolanensi</placeName> miles.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8114">Balingketus</persName> affirmat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Das ein fändli lyt noch zuͦ <persName type="auto_name">Rovere</persName> 2 myl under <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107">Drient</placeName>, daa ettliche der obersten gefangen.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Hall</placeName> im <placeName type="auto_name">Ynthal</placeName> stirbt es redlich.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Das waßer hett hin und wider in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> großen schaden gethon.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Novi praeterea nihil habemus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Italia nobis clausa est propter pestem; itaque <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8114">Balingketus</persName> affirmat caseos illos, quos petit d. d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8075" cert="high">Erastus</persName>, nunc comparari non posse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si tu prior ad d. d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8075" cert="high">Erastum</persName> scribis, eum de hoc toto edoce.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, reverende in Christo pater, cum tuis omnibus quam felicissime et diutissime.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Si scribis, adde more solito collegae salutem, ne per me suspicetur sua elata esse; sinam, ut ipse se prodat suo tempore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię</placeName> 24. iulii anno 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8009" cert="high">Fabricius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">F litera redundabat et in caeteris desiderabantur quaedam; itaque mitto tibi hoc folium, ut habeas gustum et videas qua litera excusa; noli remittere; non opus habeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amplissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino suo et in Christo patri reverendo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zurich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[<placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Zürich</placeName> StA, E II 375, 745; Hiezu ein Blatt:]</note>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Disputationes adversus protestationem triginta quatuor haereticorum <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustanae</placeName> confessionis habita a <persName type="auto_name">Gasparo Cardillo</persName>, Villalpandaeo, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispano</placeName> Segobiensi, doctore theologo, pro sacra oecumenica synodo <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentina</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Simul etiam redditur ratio multorum, quae in eadem sacra synodo contigerunt.</s>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad illustrissimum reverendum dominum <persName type="auto_name">Carolum Borromaeum</persName>, S.R.E. presbyterum cardinalem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum privilegio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l522">Venetiis</placeName> apud Donatum Bertellum 1564.</s>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sunt disputationes 9, quarum titulos, si vis, alias mittam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="32" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haeretici, qui partim exprofesso, partim obiter a nobis confutantur in his disputationibus: Triginta quatuor protestantes, superintendentes <placeName ref="l210" cert="high">Heydelbergae</placeName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1974" cert="high">Luther</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2095" cert="high">Melanchton</persName>, <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Fabricius Montanus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3375">Vergerius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name">Wiclefus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p5327">Ussus</persName>, Pragensis, <persName type="auto_name">Nicolaus Gallus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2336">Ochinus</persName>, <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Petrus Martyr</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3018">Stancar</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4091" cert="high">Zvinglius</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Svenchfeldius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p458" cert="high">Brentius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name">Pomeranus</persName>, <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingerus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinus</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Sleydanus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name">Dorpius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p5565" cert="high">Capito</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name">Monhemus</persName>, Confessio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18" cert="high">Augustana</placeName>, <persName ref="p6210" cert="high">Urbanus Rhegius</persName> Prefatur in hunc libro primo ipse author, deinde <persName type="citizen_name">Iacobus Gibertus</persName>, episcopus <placeName type="citizen_name">Aliphanus</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="33" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic authorem miris laudibus effert, ut praecipuum Lutheromastyga.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="34" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Appellat me religionis pontificiae desertorem et transfugam, quasi vero unquam illarum partium fuerim, qui transfugerim.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
